Élodie Frenck https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%89lodie_Frenck 0 Élodie Frenck is a Peruvian-Swiss-French actress, born 31 July 1974 in Lausanne, Switzerland. She is known for playing the character of Marlène Leroy in the French TV series Les Petits Meurtres d'Agatha Christie.
